{"tid":1779452,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[攬炒] 聖誕新年想攬炒，必須重啓「和你Sing」商場戰線","createTime":"2019-12-11T16:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T12:31:49.000Z","uid":159913,"like":143,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"7e46ab7e7d36863afc6411f45ac86a405709d5ce","tid":1779452,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:18:14.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢排商場多返人行，淺黃同港豬再次進入食玩買mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但咁樣點撚樣五大訴求啫? 好多人開始唔記得呢半年發生嘅事，政府民望回升，係咪要有人提佢哋呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以要零售市道冧檔，除咗拒絕消費之外仲要重啓「和你Sing」<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聖誕新年做唔到生意啲名店一定蝕撚到仆街，唔係唔做吓話?</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好處:<br />\n低成本抗爭<br />\n可集氣聚民意<br />\n各區都有商場可以join，參加門檻極低<br />\n可以引黑警發癲破壞社會秩序<br />\n建造業工人有工開(optional)<br />\n<br />\n最後同大家回顧吓當時9月份「和你Sing」活動，希望出日程表即刻各區一齊搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-xuZSHCVaE4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-xuZSHCVaE4&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAEcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=20ffdeb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-xuZSHCVaE4</a>"},{"pid":"5fb6b22a61a574fa4a82bc73066d30e7b95adcf5","tid":1779452,"uid":4739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:19:51.000Z","msg":"真。經濟攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf067c4edff7dcea6a9492d2f5f1d6ac00db27f","tid":1779452,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe6e94c4b106f68ce70dd35e7a6785bdce2af4e","tid":1779452,"uid":159913,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"遊行晒完一次馬，要繼續去商場晒<img src